STATE
v.
Rodney Moucell JONES. No. 271P14-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Nov. 25, 2015. Rodney Moucell Jones, Spruce Pine, for Jones, Rodney Moucell. Joseph L. Hyde, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Todd Williams, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 24th of November 2015 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 25th of November 2015."
